60000 atoms in group hydrogen

mass            1 10.811
mass            2 14.007
mass            3 15.9994
mass            4 1.008

pair_coeff      1 1 0.050 3.40
pair_coeff      2 2 0.050 3.40
pair_coeff      3 3 0.1521 3.1507
pair_coeff      4 4 0.0000 0.0000
pair_coeff      1 2 0.050 3.40
pair_coeff      1 3 0.050 3.30
pair_coeff      1 4 0.0000 0.0000
